  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avenir Tower is a straightforward platforming/parkour game where you attempt to reach the top of a giant structure known as the Avenir Tower. With secret locations, multiple types of obstacles and unforgiving jumps, its simple concept will prove to be a challenge to all.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game does not have a save option and is meant to be completed in one straight run, where each jump is a new advance and each fall  a new beginning. Now go and JUMP, FALL, AND JUMP AGAIN.</p>",
